flowchart TD
    U[Discord User] --> C[/ask question]
    C --> D[Discord.js Client]
    D --> H[interactionHandler.js]

    H --> R{Rate limited?}
    R -- Yes --> RL[Ephemeral cooldown response]
    R -- No --> DEF[deferReply]

    DEF --> M[memoryService.js]
    M -->|Supabase configured| DB[(Supabase app_chat_history)]
    M -->|No Supabase env| IM[(In-memory conversationStore)]

    DEF --> KC[courseClient.js]
    KC --> SK[Static Rutgers CS seed requirements]
    KC --> SC[Relevant course search]
    SK --> CTX[Course context block]
    SC --> CTX

    M --> HIST[Short-term history]
    HIST --> AI[aiClient.js]
    CTX --> AI
    AI --> OAI[OpenAI Chat Completion]
    OAI --> RESP[Course planning response]

    RESP --> SPLIT[messageUtils.splitMessage]
    SPLIT --> ER[editReply first chunk]
    SPLIT --> FU[followUp remaining chunks]

    RESP --> SAVE[saveMemoryAsync]
    SAVE --> DB
    SAVE --> IM

    subgraph Future Integrations
        WEBREG[WebReg / Schedule of Classes]
        RMP[RateMyProfessor / difficulty data]
        CATALOG[Rutgers catalog / Degree Navigator export]
        RAG[Vector search / RAG store]
    end

    WEBREG -. replaces or extends .-> KC
    RMP -. enriches .-> KC
    CATALOG -. canonical requirements .-> KC
    RAG -. retrieval layer .-> CTX
